title: Fix RSS bug
message:
Fix RSS bug

Some fields are missing in one of the items in NASA's RSS feed right
now, which is causing a parsing error in SimpleXML. I've just decided to
make all of the fields optional, and if the URL or date is empty, the
image just won't be shown.

Wallpapers can now be set, some Android 4.x.x bugs have been fixed, a
bug involving Parcelables has been fixed, and other minor changes have
been made as well.

title: Rework settings and add fallback functionality
message:
Rework settings and add fallback functionality

Most of the settings have been reorganized. None of them work yet, but
that's next on the agenda.

As for the fallback functionality: now, if morph.io isn't working (for
whatever reason), then nasa.gov will be used in its place. Also, for
image downloads, if the full image doesn't exist, then the thumbnail
will be downloaded instead.

title: Use a single model for storing all data
message:
Use a single model for storing all data

Rather than storing data using three separate models (IotdRssModel,
ApodMorphIoModel, and ApodNasaGovModel), a single model is now used:
UniversalImageModel. This has simplified the code a bit and will make
storing persistent data easier in the future.
